race.comment: GOTEBO (1) resumed two weeks ago over 1000m at Clifton and was only beaten 1.5 lengths into fourth after being in the firing line on the corner. Fitter so expect a better run this time. KANTAI (5) was well supported when resuming last start but just missed the placings in fourth over 1000m at Mitchell. Has good early toe so she should be handy in the run. Should be involved in the finish. LIPSTICK LIES (6) raced below her best last time when tenth over 1400m at Gatton last start. Forgive that run. Worth consideration here. SEMPER INVICTUS (7) was beaten 4.5 lengths into ninth when resuming last start over 1000m at Clifton. Fitter and a hope.
